Uses of Computer2Space in system
 

Classes in system that implement Computer2Space
 class ComputerProxy
          Represents a thread taking tasks from the Space and sends it to the registered computers to execute it remotely and place the Result back into the Space to be fetched by the clients.
 class SpaceImpl
          Represents a computing resource which defines how (Task) are automatically executed by registered workers as soon as they are dropped into the Space.
